menu.title: Fitness Menu
menu.descr: The 'Fitness' menu is a new approach to cooking: more fresh vegetables and fruits. A product for active and healthy people. This is an absolutely new product with an optimal price and high quality!

menu.title: Lenten Menu
menu.descr: The 'Lenten' menu is a careful selection of ingredients: completely free from animal products, milk from almonds, oats, coconut, or buckwheat, the right amount of protein from tofu and imported vegetarian steaks.

menu.title: Premium Menu
menu.descr: In the 'Premium' menu, we use not only beautiful packaging design but also high-quality dish execution. Red fish, seafood, fruits - a restaurant menu without going to the restaurant!
